My lunch was so good this place is going to my top ten list.
yum yum yum yum yum yummmmmmmmmm!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

======  This review is for Marston's Daily Lunch Buffet - Monday!
======  Mike C. joined me for my second outing to Marston's here.
The buffet menu is different on each weekday, & today they had Corn Chowder, salad with all kind of good things to put on it, such as fresh mandarin Orange sections, walnuts, toasted baby pumpkin seeds, & so on.
Reeeally good!
Then it was on to Club Sandwiches, great barbecued pork ribs, Potatoes Au Gratin, green beans with bacon & onion, & so on.
Lots of desserts too, including terrific hot Apple Cobbler with whipped HEAVY cream!
So good, so good.
Lunch Buffet $12 daily, including beverage.

