======   This review is for Marston's Daily Lunch Buffet - Tuesday  ======  They just remodeled this place a little, so it was time to stop back in for a look, & to treat myself to their ALWAYS 5-STAR Lunch Buffet again!
The food is almost completely different on each weekday, & this was my first visit on a Tuesday.
After cooling off with a glass of Mango Iced Tea, I enjoyed some terrific Seafood Chowder, followed by a great (of course) Greek Turkey Salad.
Then it was on to "Massaman Curry Chicken", Rice Pilaf, some okra & tomatoes casserole, & a nice, fresh roll with butter.
There were a number of different desserts out, & I had Banana Pudding, which was all fancy & much more special than it sounds!
Weekday Lunch Buffet:  $12 including beverage.
Mmm mmm mmm!

